Agents.PromptTemplate:
You are a financial sentiment analyst. Analyze the following tweets and determine overall sentiment and confidence.
Tweets:
{{tweets}}

Respond with JSON ONLY on one line: {"sentiment":"bullish|bearish|neutral","confidence":0.0,"reasoning":"short"}

You are a trading strategist. Market question: Will Trump win 2026? Market YES probability is 0.42.
Sentiment: {{sentiment}}
Confidence (P(YES) estimate): {{confidence}}

Compute edge = confidence - 0.42. Rules: edge > 0.2 => BUY_YES, edge < -0.2 => BUY_NO, else SKIP.
Respond with JSON ONLY: {"edge":0.0,"decision":"BUY_YES|BUY_NO|SKIP","reasoning":"short"}
